Java, Minecraft Plugin Developer

I'm a Java Developer that specializes in Minecraft Spigot Plugin Development. I started coding in Java in August 2019. I made all sorts of minigames, utility, and core plugins for my clients while making sure that they have no major bugs and are lag-free. I use two databases to store player/server data: MySQL, MongoDB and Redis to achieve cross-server communication. Also, I used many APIs such as JDA (Java Discord API), Vault (Economy), NBTAPI (Changing item/entities NBT tags) and a lot more, basically whatever you want me to do, I will do it.
